Fortune centre have so many options for food and beverages including restaurants with different foreign and local cuisines in Singapore. The established dessert store Yat Ka Ran served the best ice shavings with Brown sugar & chendol. Walnut cream and ice shaving with mango ice cream, pamelo and dliced mangoes are actually delicious. These pictures were taken on the 30th of December, 2024.

Fortune Center is a health-oriented mall with several floors of Chinese and western medicine shops, about 10 veg restaurants (mostly Chinese, but also Indian and Japanese), a veg grocery store, as well as various other shops and restaurants. Surprising their bread is good! They make it warmly nice to chew.
